OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPope Francis: Pontiff says 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhe is 'deeply sorry' to    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FCanadian residential school
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In his first public remarks in Canada, 
OL,6, Pope Francis has asked indigenous      
OL,7, residential school survivors for       
OL,8, forgiveness.                           
OL,10,F"I am deeply sorry," the Pope said on  
OL,11,Fthe grounds of a former residential    
OL,12,Fschool in Maskwacis, near Edmonton.    
OL,14,FHe said his apology is a first step,   
OL,15,Fand that a "serious investigation" into
OL,16,Fabuses must occur to foster healing.   
OL,18,FThe pontiff is in Canada to apologise  
OL,19,Ffor the Church's role in schools meant 
OL,20,Fto assimilate indigenous children.     
